1 5. Rules. The commissioner shall adopt rules to carry out the purposes of this section.
2 Rules adopted pursuant to this subsection are routine technical rules under Title 5, chapter
3 375, subchapter 2-A.
4 Sec. 3. Commissioner of Education to form committee. By January 15, 2026,
5 the Commissioner of Education shall make the appointments to the Learning Results
6 Implementation Advisory Committee under the Maine Revised Statutes, Title 20-A,
7 section 14 and convene the first meeting of the committee.
8 Sec. 4. Appropriations and allocations. The following appropriations and
9 allocations are made.
